altername_name: Ginga Ojousama Densetsu Yuna: Akitaka Mika IllustWorks
name: Ginga Ojousama Densetsu Yuna Mika Akitaka Illust Works
overview: Ginga Ojousama Densetsu Yuna Mika Akitaka Illust Works (銀河お嬢様伝説 ユナ あきたか みか イラストワークス) is an art gallery for the Sega Saturn. It was followed by Ginga Ojousama Densetsu Yuna Mika Akitaka Illust Works 2.
